data: The dark source dried up my body and crushed the bones, relieved the bones of nerves.
The body is no longer one, the whole force has gone out and there is no more sound.

There was so much knowledge, and my consciousness slipped away, broke, split, gradually all my thoughts fell apart into pieces, just a dance, just a dance of consciousnesses of moments and ringing and laughter.
I have no reason to live anymore, today I will leave forever...
I couldn't feed the symbiotic creatures, and now they are very hungry. A little more and they will break out of my body and disembowel everyone around.

The portal was closed before I could leave the oasis. Gradually, the features of my body distorted. The skin became softer and darker, yellow pupils and large fangs appeared in the eyes. Now I'm not from this world at all.
My heart is no longer beating, now I don't have the strength to saturate my fingers with even a little bit of wind.
